_sText: Intro: Hi, most of all players like the dust maps. So i asked Rikku to make me a small version of de_dust for my gungame server. After many versions and bugfixes here comes the final one. It also has buyzones - so it can be used for other small servers, too. Also: a new tunnel and a teleport spawn from t to ct spanpoint at the doors. You can try it on our: GUNGAME SERVER - its in the mapcycle ^^ Its one of Rikkus first mapworks, so please be nice to her work :-) Infos from Rikku: rebell_dust_mini for Counter-Strike: Source - 30.01.2007 Change by Rikku2000 with help from [amz|Mc$core] Original Map by Valve! Installation Notes: Extract the files to the cstrike directory. The files will be placed into. eg: Steam/SteamApps/User Account/counter-strike source/cstrike/
